### Existing Infrastructure

| Component | File | Role |
|-----------|------|------|
| `PortAllocator` | `packages/core/src/deploy/port-allocator.ts` | Allocates/releases ports from preview range (4000-4999) |
| `CaddyClient` | `packages/core/src/routing/caddy.ts` | Adds/removes reverse proxy routes via Caddy admin API |
